{{docs-hero
  logo="ember"
  slimHeading="FilePond"
  byline="A handy FilePond adapter component for Ember"}}

<div class="docs-container docs-md">
  <section class="docs-section docs-max-w-md docs-mx-auto docs-pb-8">
    <img src="https://cdn.rawgit.com/alexdiliberto/ember-filepond/master/tests/dummy/public/filepond-logo.svg" alt="FilePond Logo" class="docs-block docs-w-full docs-mx-auto docs-my-4">

    <h2>Introduction</h2>

    <p><a href="https://pqina.nl/filepond/">FilePond</a> is a JavaScript library that can upload anything you throw at it, optimizes images for faster uploads, and offers a great, accessible, silky smooth user experience. This addon is an adapter to use with your Ember applications.</p>

    <div class="docs-my-5 docs-text-right">
      {{#docs-link "docs"}}
        <button class="
          docs-bg-grey-darkest docs-text-white docs-py-2 docs-px-4 docs-no-underline docs-rounded
          hover:docs-bg-black
        ">
          Get started &rarr;
        </button>
      {{/docs-link}}
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
